{"tid":1506694,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣戰新方向 - 推個波落大陸仔到","createTime":"2019-08-26T01:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T03:29:13.000Z","uid":89994,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49a4b652d0adba40728224ee84d7e8aeb6ebf66e","tid":1506694,"uid":89994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:23:23.000Z","msg":"講起文宣戰 琴晚諗住鳩up串下藍絲父母<br />\n鳩up 話搞亂香港係大陸搞出黎（實質都係，不過佢地不嬲屈落美國佬）<br />\n話要搞冧香港搵深圳同上海代替<br />\n不過諗諗下， 點解唔用多個新方向去做<br />\n運動行左兩個月 已經唔係單純推翻一條條例既層面<br />\n不如用下而面既point 去做文宣<br />\n-香港人養唔熟，唔認做支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-外資唔可以直接監管，所以美國先咁驚香港搞唔掂<br />\n因為一國兩制先放好多錢係香港到<br />\n唔想直接投資放d錢放上海深圳<br />\n-再加上搞上海深圳自由貿易區都冇成績，交唔到功課<br />\n<br />\n歡迎後補<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw, 食早餐無意聽到格離d呀伯屌鳩d後生仔<br />\n本身以為係廢老黎 點知佢地話 :<br />\n有竹都唔撚識用 佢地拎支棍咁撚短<br />\n一支竹篤落佢心口到<br />\n篤佢老母臭閪咪搞撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7edd713ece1fecafcf168a4e766865fca2da5c8","tid":1506694,"uid":29899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:23:38.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=5b9a350e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />